profile:
TLC was founded by Tyler Ford at the age of 15. Starting out by mowing lawns for neighbors during high school, it eventually grew to a small business. By 2018, Tylerâ€™s Lawn Care & Snow Removal was serving over 100 valued clients in the Halifax, Bedford & Sackville area. TLC offers an array of year-round services including:

- Lawn Mowing
- Lawn Care
- Weed Control
- Pest Control
- Gardening
- Landscape Maintenance
- Residential Landscape Installs
- Seasonal Clean-Ups
- Snow Removal
